<html>
<body>
<p>
  Your organization has been invited by <%=@invitation.inviter.name%> to join CompSage.
</p>
<p>
  CompSage allows HR professionals to send quick compensation surveys to organizations of their choosing. 
</p>
<p>
  With CompSage you can:
  <ul>  
    <li>Design surveys using our standard questions or add questions of your own desgin.</li>
    <li>Participate in a survey and get results for free. Sponsor a survey for $100 and get great data that won't put you over-budget.</li>
    <li>Survey turnaround in as little as 3 days.</li>
    <li>Guaranteed results, otherwise you will not pay a cent.</li>
    <li>Access compensation data in use right now by the companies of your choosing.</li>
  </ul>  
</p>
<p>
  Becoming a member of CompSage is easy and free! To get started, please  
  <% if @network.nil? then %>
    <%=link_to "click here", new_account_path(:key => @invitation.key, :only_path => false)%>.
  <% else %>
      <%=link_to "click here", new_account_path(:key => @invitation.key, :network_id => @network.id, :only_path => false)%>.
  <% end %>
</p>
<p>
  Thanks,
  <br />
  CompSage.com
</p>
</body>
</html>
